Sentencas: A porous NiO/yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) anode substrate for zirconia-based tubular solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) was prepared by the gelcasting.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The effect of the impregnation of SDC in the substrate was studied.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy and I-V and I-P curves of the cells were measured.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscopy (SEM) was used to observe the microstructures.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results indicate that the performance of the cell can be significantly improved by incorporating the nano-structured SDC particles in the substrate.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The peak power density of the cell is increased by about 60% and the area specific resistance (ASR) decreased by about 47% at 700 degrees C, compared with the unmodified cells.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: It is explained as the extended triple-phase boundary (TPB) in the anode substrate and the excellent electrocatalytic property of SDC.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: It is also found that the nano-scale SDC particles change a lot during the reduction of the anode substrate, and the morphology of the resultant SDC particles on the metal Ni is significantly different from that on the YSZ.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: After the long-term operation, the morphology of the SDC particles on the Ni changes again, but that on the YSZ keeps almost unchanged.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of Sm-doped CeO2 in NiO/YSZ anode substrate prepared by gelcasting for tubular solid oxide fuel cell
